<text x="70" y="116" font-size="18" fill="#695b51" style='font-family: "Noto Sans SC", "Microsoft YaHei", "PingFang SC", Arial, sans-serif;'>样本量 n=57，以18-25岁女性学生为主；用于呈现青年养宠群体倾向。</text>
<text x='80' y='181' font-size='22' fill='#2d241f' style='font-family: "Noto Sans SC", "Microsoft YaHei", "PingFang SC", Arial, sans-serif;'>略有耳闻</text><rect x='295' y='150' width='533.4' height='42' rx='10' fill='#d8b88f'/><rect x='295' y='150' width='533.4' height='42' rx='10' fill='url(#g)' opacity='.75'/><text x='848.4' y='180' font-size='22' fill='#683a2a' font-weight='800' style='font-family: "Noto Sans SC", "Microsoft YaHei", "PingFang SC", Arial, sans-serif;'>70.18%</text><text x='80' y='253' font-size='22' fill='#2d241f' style='font-family: "Noto Sans SC", "Microsoft YaHei", "PingFang SC", Arial, sans-serif;'>首选专业火化</text><rect x='295' y='222' width='386.7' height='42' rx='10' fill='#d8b88f'/><rect x='295' y='222' width='386.7' height='42' rx='10' fill='url(#g)' opacity='.75'/><text x='701.7' y='252' font-size='22' fill='#683a2a' font-weight='800' style='font-family: "Noto Sans SC", "Microsoft YaHei", "PingFang SC", Arial, sans-serif;'>50.88%</text><text x='80' y='325' font-size='22' fill='#2d241f' style='font-family: "Noto Sans SC", "Microsoft YaHei", "PingFang SC", Arial, sans-serif;'>反对自行掩埋</text><rect x='295' y='294' width='560.0' height='42' rx='10' fill='#d8b88f'/><rect x='295' y='294' width='560.0' height='42' rx='10' fill='url(#g)' opacity='.75'/><text x='875.0' y='324' font-size='22' fill='#683a2a' font-weight='800' style='font-family: "Noto Sans SC", "Microsoft YaHei", "PingFang SC", Arial, sans-serif;'>73.68%</text><text x='80' y='397' font-size='22' fill='#2d241f' style='font-family: "Noto Sans SC", "Microsoft YaHei", "PingFang SC", Arial, sans-serif;'>重视价格透明</text><rect x='295' y='366' width='653.3' height='42' rx='10' fill='#d8b88f'/><rect x='295' y='366' width='653.3' height='42' rx='10' fill='url(#g)' opacity='.75'/><text x='968.3' y='396' font-size='22' fill='#683a2a' font-weight='800' style='font-family: "Noto Sans SC", "Microsoft YaHei", "PingFang SC", Arial, sans-serif;'>85.96%</text><text x='80' y='469' font-size='22' fill='#2d241f' style='font-family: "Noto Sans SC", "Microsoft YaHei", "PingFang SC", Arial, sans-serif;'>认为价格混乱</text><rect x='295' y='438' width='613.3' height='42' rx='10' fill='#d8b88f'/><rect x='295' y='438' width='613.3' height='42' rx='10' fill='url(#g)' opacity='.75'/><text x='928.3' y='468' font-size='22' fill='#683a2a' font-weight='800' style='font-family: "Noto Sans SC", "Microsoft YaHei", "PingFang SC", Arial, sans-serif;'>80.70%</text><text x='80' y='541' font-size='22' fill='#2d241f' style='font-family: "Noto Sans SC", "Microsoft YaHei", "PingFang SC", Arial, sans-serif;'>担心资质不规范</text><rect x='295' y='510' width='520.0' height='42' rx='10' fill='#d8b88f'/><rect x='295' y='510' width='520.0' height='42' rx='10' fill='url(#g)' opacity='.75'/><text x='835.0' y='540' font-size='22' fill='#683a2a' font-weight='800' style='font-family: "Noto Sans SC", "Microsoft YaHei", "PingFang SC", Arial, sans-serif;'>68.42%</text><text x='80' y='613' font-size='22' fill='#2d241f' style='font-family: "Noto Sans SC", "Microsoft YaHei", "PingFang SC", Arial, sans-serif;'>期待政府监管</text><rect x='295' y='582' width='440.0' height='42' rx='10' fill='#d8b88f'/><rect x='295' y='582' width='440.0' height='42' rx='10' fill='url(#g)' opacity='.75'/><text x='755.0' y='612' font-size='22' fill='#683a2a' font-weight='800' style='font-family: "Noto Sans SC", "Microsoft YaHei", "PingFang SC", Arial, sans-serif;'>57.89%</text>
